item.title: [AWS]AWS DEA Services
item.description: Data EngineeringData engineering is the development, implementation, and maintenance of processes and systems that ingest raw data and produce high quality and consistent data to be used for analysis , machine learning, and more. As a data engineer, you must incorporate security, data management, orchestration, data architecture, software engineering , and operations to manage the lifecycle of data. The goal is to take raw data and make it easy and reliable to work with and to integrate across datasets and domains.
